# .dev.vars.example
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This is the ".env.example" for this project. Cloudflare Workers read local
# secrets from a file named ".dev.vars" (same idea as a .env file).
#
# Setup:
#   1. Copy this file to ".dev.vars"      ->  cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars
#   2. Put your real key in ".dev.vars"   (that file is git-ignored)
#   3. Never commit ".dev.vars" or the real key.
#
# For the DEPLOYED Worker (production), you do NOT use this file. Instead run:
#   npx wrangler secret put FINNHUB_API_KEY
#
# Get a free API key at https://finnhub.io

FINNHUB_API_KEY=your_finnhub_api_key_here
